cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO

The paper proposes a method for human pose estimation using Deep Neural Networks (DNNs), which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The approach is based on recent advances in Deep Learning (cs.LG) and involves formulating the pose estimation as a regression problem (cs.AI). The method is evaluated on real-world images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) applications.
